FinalCodeFactoryIF
public class FinalCodeFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements FinalCodeFactoryIF

Factory of final code. This class create a file with final code by invoking the translate method of an ExecutionEnvironment for each Quadruple found in the intermediate code.
